# Installation
## Termux
```

apt update && apt upgrade
pkg install python
pkg install git
git clone https://github.com/STARK-404/FB-HACK/
cd FB-HACK 
pip install -r requirments.txt
python Run.py
```
## Linux
```
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade
sudo apt install python3
git clone https://github.com/STARK-404/FB-HACK/
cd FB-HACK 
pip install -r requirements.txt
python3 Run.py
```
